@baseUrl = http://localhost:8082

### Get user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/user1

### Batch get users
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nt_accounts": ["user1", "user2", "user1"]
}

### Empty user list returns 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nt_accounts": []
}

### Empty account returns 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user-list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nt_accounts": ["user1", ""]
}
